text = "[font_size=28][color=#FFD54F]Controls[/color][/font_size]
[color=#81C784]Left-click[/color] Select objects
[color=#81C784]Right-click[/color] Command selected units to [b]Move[/b], [b]Gather[/b] and [b]Attack[/b]
[color=#64B5F6]WASDQE[/color] Move camera
[color=#81C784]Shift Right-click[/color] Queue Up commands
[color=#64B5F6]Scroll Wheel[/color] Zoom camera

[font_size=28][color=#FFD54F]Objective[/color][/font_size]
Defeat the [color=#FF8A65][b]Big Elephant[/b][/color] within [color=#FF5252][b]8 minutes[/b][/color].

[font_size=28][color=#FFD54F]Tips[/color][/font_size]
Collect [color=#FDD835][b]Honey Blobs[/b][/color] for [color=#FDD835][b]12 Honey[/b][/color] each.
